{"tid":1791577,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彥霖離世三月 市民拒絕遺忘","createTime":"2019-12-21T03:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T03:37:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b45a1a20e5e2eb3aff98280cb265252f9949d5ee","tid":1791577,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191221/6IS6QGWKVLV4ZTDKLEL3XJNWR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191221%2F6IS6QGWKVLV4ZTDKLEL3XJNWR4%2F&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQRX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=49fa4b12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191221%2F6IS6QGWKVLV4ZTDKLEL3XJNWR4%2F&h=cba8a1e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191221/6IS6QGWKVLV4ZTDKLEL3XJNWR4/</a><br />\n<br />\n彥霖離世三月 市民拒絕遺忘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191221/large/1576858195_f5d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576858195_f5d8.jpg&h=268b5b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民昨到將軍澳拜祭彥霖，冀為她尋回公道。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】15歲女生陳彥霖9月被發現全裸伏屍在油塘魔鬼山海面。她生前是游泳健將，亦曾參與反修例運動，外界一直懷疑其死因並非意外，甚至與警方有關。有網民昨午在尚德邨停車場外舉行彥霖追思會，悼念彥霖離世三個月。有專程前來致祭的市民稱到場<span style=\"color: orange;\">是為了警惕自己不要因聖誕的假日氣氛而淡忘抗爭，要謹記港人在整場運動中的犧牲。</span><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：踢保教師轟警濫捕致準則不公<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「聖誕唔好做隻港豬」<br />\n<br />\n追思會下午3點在尚德邨停車場外唐明街行人路上舉行。該處早前有市民自行設立祭壇，悼念陳彥霖及早前疑因躲避警方催淚彈而失足墮斃的科大學生周梓樂。記者現場所見，多名市民帶備香燭及鮮花到場拜祭，不少人致祭期間神色哀傷。<br />\n<br />\n到場致祭的Joesph表示，參加追思會是要警惕自己不要淡忘整場運動，「<span style=\"color: orange;\">喺呢個聖誕假期唔好掛住去玩，唔好做隻港豬，我哋有更多嘢可以做到。</span>」當提及對彥霖死因時，Joesph更不滿警方指彥霖死因沒可疑的說法，「（警方）查都冇&times;查過，點樣冇可疑呢，真係好荒謬。」他指，不少港人會像他一樣，會代彥霖走下去，願她在天之靈可以安息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191221/large/1576858194_ba66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576858194_ba66.jpg&h=b215acea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n悼念者留下對彥霖的哀思。<br />\n<br />\n銀髮族Wendy亦專程坐車到場拜祭彥霖。她對彥霖如此年輕便香消玉殞感到惋惜，更認為她的<span style=\"color: orange;\">死因是至今仍不明不白，「有好多問號，要繼續追查，（港人）唔可以不了了之」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Wendy續稱，過去數月一想起大批年輕人因參與反修例示威而被捕、被打，便十分痛心，乃至無法安睡，「一諗起個心就好痛，雖然（他們）唔係自己仔女，但（他們）都係香港人」。</span><br />\n<br />\n■記者羅智堅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a29a5b1c6be3fcb1be7ccfae05f4ad959ec0ee","tid":1791577,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5652769b60ab8bb8f38ef0e2beb523a4c446c804","tid":1791577,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">杜絕政治酬庸<br />\n銀髮族集會</span><br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間:下午1時至5時<br />\n地點:愛丁堡廣場大會堂對出空地<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對通知書</span><br />\nfacebook銀髮族老而不廢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">毋忘721恐襲<br />\nRemembering 721 Terror</span><br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間 : 15:00<br />\n地點: <br />\n- 元朗 YOНО MALL<br />\n- 尖沙咀 海港城"},{"pid":"0b40cf06088b4c06a5bacbac998d2f0d04065e51","tid":1791577,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea155caf635a4bf24adf22e55c6cd8e2cf6284d4","tid":1791577,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:24:55.000Z